### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:3001/api/health

### 查所有记录
GET http://localhost:3001/api/records

### 查统计（余额）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/summary

### 新增一条记录（支出/餐饮/200）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 111,
  "category": "餐饮",
  "date": "2026-07-13",
  "note": "测试新增"
}

### 按 id 查单条（把 1 换成实际 id）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/records/50

### 修改记录（把 1 换成实际 id）
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/records/50
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 888.5,
  "category": "餐饮",
  "date": "2026-07-13",
  "note": "改过的备注"
}

### 删除记录（把 1 换成实际 id）
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/records/50
